com.facebook.buck.remoteexecution.util

Class MerkleTreeNodeCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.remoteexecution.util.MerkleTreeNodeCache

  • public class MerkleTreeNodeCache
extends Object
    MerkleTreeNodeCache is used to create and merge merkle trees for action inputs. The nodes are interned.

    It also provides methods to get the Protocol encoded merkle tree data structures (these values are cached once computed for a node).
